Package ConsList

Class Summary
Cons Cons defines a nonempty ConsList, containing a head and a tail.
ConsList ConsList defines the data type of cons-lists: a Nil cons-list will be modelled by new Nil(); a Cons cons-list will be modelled by new Cons(h, t).
ListOps ListOps define some standard operations for processing ConsLists
Nil Nil defines an empty ConsList
TestList TestList shows a few experiments with ConsLists
